snippet.textDisplay: I just 'liked' the song because it brought back all the memories from so many years ago. I still remember when the band had performed at Filmfare awards in India (Mumbai) and took the entire Bollywood and city by storm (they were of course famous already through MTV). I love Rahat saab but this rendition just doesn't cut it. It does not have the overflowing josh, the energy the original had. Sorry, I expected more. A bit disappointed.
snippet.textOriginal: I just 'liked' the song because it brought back all the memories from so many years ago. I still remember when the band had performed at Filmfare awards in India (Mumbai) and took the entire Bollywood and city by storm (they were of course famous already through MTV). I love Rahat saab but this rendition just doesn't cut it. It does not have the overflowing josh, the energy the original had. Sorry, I expected more. A bit disappointed.
